title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update IV - Amsterdam
description:
In this video we will look at the city of Amsterdam which has been updated  part of World Update IV: France/Benelux which has been released today. We are using our H135 chopper to fly over the city. Based on some testing with video settings it looks a bit choppy a some moments so I still have some work to do optimizing the settings again after this new update.
